      "text": "みなさん、こんにちは！\n今日は、来てくれてありがとうございます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello everyone!\nThanks for coming out to see us today!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.966666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 7.033333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_04-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "今日、決勝を戦うにあたって\n私達は話し合いました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As we prepared to compete in the finals today‚\nwe did some talking.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.866666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_04-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "お互いが全力で力を出し切るには\nどうしたらいいか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We wanted to give our best performances and give it our all.\nSo we asked‚ what should we do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.933333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 16.133333333333297
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_04-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたら後悔がないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How can we have no regrets?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.133333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 18.333333333333336
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
