      "text": "お互い、一番歌いたいのは……\n見せたいパフォーマンスはなんなのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We all thought about the song we wanted to sing the most…\nthe performance we most wanted to give…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.133333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
