      "text": "メンバー同士、意見を交換し、何度も話し合い\nそしてこうしようと決めました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "All the group members gave their input. We talked through it‚ over and over‚\nand we finally arrived at this decision.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.666666666666675,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
